{
  "verses": [
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Lewiteeni/ uṣrakſtija tohs ta Reh- \nnixa Preekſcha/ un preekſch teem \nLeeleein-Kungeein/ un preekſch to \nPreeſtert Zadakn/ un preekſch A- \nkimeleku Abjatara Dehlu/ un \npreekſch teem Wirfneekem to \nTehwo Namnu/starp teem Pree- \nstereem un starp teem Lewiteem/ \nweens Tehwa Nams tappe \nneits preekſch Geleasaru/ un \nweens ta patt tappe neits \npreekſch Ihtamaru.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "7. Un ta pirma Meſloſchanas \nSihme tikke Jojaribanu/ ta oh- \ntra Jedajam.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "8. Ta trescha Ariman/ta zet- \ntorta Seorinam.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "9. Ta peekta Malkijam/ ta \nfesta Mejamimam.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "10. Ta feptita Akozam/ ta \nastota Abijam.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "11. Ta dewita Jesuam/ ta \ndefinita Sekanijam.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "12. Ta weenpadefinita Elia- \nsibam/ ta divipadefinita Jaki- \nman.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "13. Ta treschapadefinita U- \npam/ ta zettortapadefinita Jese- \nbeabam.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "14. Ta peektapadefinita Bil- \ngam/ ta testapadefinita Jineram.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "15. Ta feptitapadefinita E- \nsram/ ta astotapadefinita Api- \nzezam.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "16. Ta dewitapadefinita Pe- \ntajam/ ta dividefinita Jeſkelam.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "17. Ta dividefinita pirma \nJakinaam/ ta dividefinita ohtra \nGamulaam.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "18. Ta dividefinita trescha \n"
    },
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Delajam/ ta dividefinita zett \nta Määsijam.\n19. Schi ir winnu Kab \npehz winnu Kalpoſchanas/ ka \nta KUNGA Namnā eetu p \nfawn Teefu femm Aarōnu fa \nTehwu/ ittin ka tam tas KU \nIsraēta Deews bij pawehlejs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 20,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "20. Un no teem zitteem Le \nja Behrneem/ no Amrama Be \nneem bija Subaēls. No Su \neka Behrneem bija Jekdejus.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 21,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "21. Starp Rebabeja B \nneembija Jesijus tas Wirfuee\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 22,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "22. No teem Jezearitex \nbija: Slomots. No Slom \nBehrneem bija: Jakats.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 23,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "23. Un no (Webrona) B \nneem bija: Jerijus tas ( \nmajs/) Amarijus tas ohtr \nJaēſiels tas treschajs/ Ja \nams tas zettortajs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 24,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "24. Uſiēta Behrni bija: \nkus. No Mikus Behrneeu \nja/ Samirs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 25,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "25. Mikus Brahtis bija: \nsjus. No Jesijus Behrneen \nja: Sakarijs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 26,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "26. Merara Behrni b \nMaēlus un Musus/ ta D \nbija: Jaēſijs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 27,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "27. Merara Behrni bija \nJaēſija winna Dehla/ Soa \nun Sakurs/ un Ibrus.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 28,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "28. No Maēlus bija: E \nfars/ jo tam ne bija Behrn \n"
    },
    {
      "n": 29,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "29. Riſa Behrni bija \n"
    },
    {
      "n": 30,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "30. Un Musus Behrni \n"
    }
  ],
